iGEM2017

Class LuxSensor

  • java.lang.Object
    • iGEM2017.LuxSensor

  • public class LuxSensor
extends java.lang.Object
    A class which allows readings from a TCS34725 lux (light) sensor connected to the Raspberry Pi I2C data pins.
